---
permalink: /_redirects
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
layout: false
---
{# POKA-YOKE: this template MUST live at src/_redirects.njk, NOT inside
   src/resources/. The src/resources/resources.11tydata.js cascade sets
   layout: "layouts/blog.njk", and the blog layout reads `title`/`page.date`
   under Nunjucks throwOnUndefined:true — those are undefined here and the
   build crashes. `layout: false` above is belt-and-suspenders for the same
   reason. #}
# Auto-generated. Source of truth: src/_redirects.njk.
# CF Pages reads /_redirects natively and serves real 301s.
# Do not hand-edit the build output (dist/_redirects) — change the template.
#
# Format: <from>  <to>  <status>
# Order matters: first match wins, so per-post mappings precede catch-alls.

# ── Per-post redirects (one per English resource) ─────────────────────
{% for post in collections.resources -%}
{{ post.data.legacyEnPath }}  {{ post.url }}  301
{% endfor %}
# ── Listing page ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/posts/  /resources/  301

# ── Catch-all for stray non-English URLs and anything else under /posts/
/posts/blog/*  /resources/  301
/posts/*  /resources/  301
